active runtime is located at:
	~/.config/openxr/1/active_runtime.json

no idea where it is under windows but the file name is the same

to get function pointers dlsym "xrGetInstanceProcAddr".

to create instance requires fetching functions:
- xrEnumerateInstanceExtensionProperties
- xrEnumerateApiLayerProperties
- xrCreateInstance
with nullptr instance parameter

from there on continue similar to shared vulkan

url: https://www.khronos.org/registry/OpenXR/specs/1.0/man/html/openxr.html#_xrgetinstanceprocaddr3
